零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於知醒要諗下自己將來<br />\n如果想讀建造業 應該讀邊樣？<br />\n同埋讀幾耐 邊做野邊讀都得？<br />\n求各位巴絲比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 今年廿一</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀到中五冇讀+1<br />\n做左一年part time/fulltime過生活<br />\n準備見新工<br />\n計畫緊未來<br />\n即將20歳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61aee78b59931dc6ae26a29f50a5217008ade2da","tid":277511,"uid":117543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有ive課程都要中六畢業，除左讀毅進慢慢升，無其他路，除非去建造業議會，但將來未必有ive好，因為資歷架構未必承認，而且工程系hd出黎最少都萬八，挨到工程師牌就出頭，起碼4-8萬一個月，一般慢嘅10年應該都OK</blockquote><br />\n其實上網見請學徒個啲學唔學到野<br />\n我諗緊去讀建造業好定直接做學徒<br />\n兩者又有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b23b4aa11de5fcb300e237eae7dc69253416d01","tid":277511,"uid":117543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己讀完中五就冇讀 <br />\nhea左兩年做下parttime過生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日見完新工 發覺自己係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於知醒要諗下自己將來<br />\n如果想讀建造業 應該讀邊樣？<br />\n同埋讀幾耐 邊做野邊讀都得？<br />\n求各位巴絲比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 今年廿一</blockquote><br />\n你係咪我呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀到中五冇讀+1<br />\n做左一年part time/fulltime過生活<br />\n準備見新工<br />\n計畫緊未來<br />\n即將20歳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗唔係 因為我即將二十一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid